snippet.title: The Struggle of Combat Trailer
snippet.description:
The Struggle of Combat is roguelike shooter with randomly generated levels.  Created with GameMaker Studio 2.

Get The Struggle of Combat from itch.io: https://yrbiax.itch.io/the-struggle-o...


Music and sound effects obtained from https://www.zapsplat.com


Review by Supersven: https://www.reviewsbysupersven.com/2020/08/27/the-struggle-of-combat-review/
